---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
	title='About Exavatar - The Future of Avatar Generation'
	description='Learn about Exavatar, the powerful avatar generation API built with modern web technologies. Discover our mission to make beautiful avatars accessible to everyone.'>
	<header
		class='grid-box col-[1/13] row-[3/5] grid grid-flow-row auto-rows-min content-center md:col-[3/11] md:row-[2/4]'>
		<h1 class='text-center text-3xl font-semibold'>About Exavatar</h1>
		<p class='text-md content-center text-center text-balance'>
			The future of avatar generation is here
		</p>
	</header>

	<main class='grid-box col-[2/12] row-[6/none] space-y-8 md:col-[3/11] md:row-[5/none]'>
		<section class='space-y-4'>
			<h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold'>Our Mission</h2>
			<p class='text-pretty'>
				At Exavatar, we believe that every application deserves beautiful, unique avatars. Our
				mission is to provide developers with the most powerful, flexible, and easy-to-use avatar
				generation API available today.
			</p>
			<p class='text-pretty'>
				Built with modern web technologies like Deno and Astro, Exavatar delivers lightning-fast
				performance while maintaining the highest standards of code quality and developer
				experience.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class='space-y-4'>
			<h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold'>Why Choose Exavatar?</h2>
			<div class='grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2'>
				<div class='space-y-2'>
					<h3 class='text-lg font-medium'>ðŸš€ Lightning Fast</h3>
					<p class='text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400'>
						Built on Deno's high-performance runtime, our API generates avatars in milliseconds.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class='space-y-2'>
					<h3 class='text-lg font-medium'>ðŸŽ¨ Highly Customizable</h3>
					<p class='text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400'>
						Choose from multiple styles, colors, sizes, and formats to match your brand perfectly.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class='space-y-2'>
					<h3 class='text-lg font-medium'>ðŸ”§ Developer Friendly</h3>
					<p class='text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400'>
						Simple REST API with comprehensive documentation and interactive playground.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class='space-y-2'>
					<h3 class='text-lg font-medium'>ðŸ“± Always Available</h3>
					<p class='text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400'>
						Deployed on Deno Deploy for 99.9% uptime and global edge distribution.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class='space-y-4'>
			<h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold'>Technology Stack</h2>
			<p class='text-pretty'>
				Exavatar is built with cutting-edge technologies to ensure optimal performance and developer
				experience:
			</p>
			<ul class='list-disc space-y-2 pl-6'>
				<li><strong>Deno</strong> - Modern, secure runtime for JavaScript and TypeScript</li>
				<li><strong>Astro</strong> - Fast, content-focused web framework</li>
				<li><strong>TypeScript</strong> - Type-safe development for better code quality</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Tailwind CSS</strong> - Utility-first CSS framework for rapid UI development
				</li>
				<li><strong>Deno Deploy</strong> - Serverless platform for global edge deployment</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class='space-y-4'>
			<h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold'>Open Source</h2>
			<p class='text-pretty'>
				Exavatar is proudly open source. We believe in transparency, community collaboration, and
				giving back to the developer community. You can find our source code, contribute
				improvements, or report issues on our GitHub repository.
			</p>
			<div class='flex gap-4'>
				<a
					href='https://github.com/gitchaell/exavatar'
					target='_blank'
					class='btn btn-primary'>
					View on GitHub
				</a>
				<a
					href='/docs'
					class='btn btn-secondary'>
					Read Documentation
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class='space-y-4'>
			<h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold'>Get Started</h2>
			<p class='text-pretty'>
				Ready to add beautiful avatars to your application? Get started in seconds with our simple
				API:
			</p>
			<div class='rounded-lg bg-gray-100 p-4 dark:bg-gray-800'>
				<code class='text-sm'>https://exavatar.deno.dev/api/avatar?set=animals&id=dinosaur</code>
			</div>
			<div class='flex gap-4'>
				<a
					href='/playground'
					class='btn btn-primary'>
					Try Playground
				</a>
				<a
					href='/gallery'
					class='btn btn-secondary'>
					Browse Gallery
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
